In working on the new regulation of the natural gas market, the EM aims to make the natural gas trading process as simple and user-friendly as possible.
Therefore, the most efficient and user-friendly service solution was the 'dealer-centric model' where all customer service activities are provided by the trader, with one contract, one invoice and one information and customer service point, leaving the technical aspects of the natural gas distribution system to the distribution system operator.
